<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscription Plans</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa, #c3cfe2);
            color: #333;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: #444;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .plan {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 320px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .plan:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .plan h2 {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            color: #0275d8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .plan p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: #555;
        }

        .plan p b {
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #0275d8;
        }

        .plan a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #fff;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0275d8, #5bc0de);
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .plan a:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #025aa5, #4aabd8);
        }

        /* Add responsiveness */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .plan {
                width: 90%;
                margin: 20px auto;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2.5em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Choose Your Plan</h1>
    
    <div class="plan">
        <h2>Starter Plan</h2>
        <p><b>$20/month</b></p>
        <p>Perfect for individuals or small teams to get started.</p>
        <a href="/subscribe?plan=starter">Get Started</a>
    </div>

    <div class="plan">
        <h2>Pro Plan</h2>
        <p><b>$40/month</b></p>
        <p>Great for growing teams needing more features.</p>
        <a href="/subscribe?plan=pro">Go Pro</a>
    </div>

    <div class="plan">
        <h2>Customize Plan</h2>
        <p><b>Contact Us for Pricing</b></p>
        <p>Fully customizable to meet your specific business needs.</p>
        <a href="/subscribe?plan=customize">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
